{"word":"ἵδρυσις","slug":"ἵδρυσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἵδρυσις</b></el> <el>(ἵδρῡσις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἱδρύω'><el>ἱδρύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a founding, building</i>, of temples, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>Ἑρμέω ἱδρύσιες</el> his <i>statues</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}